Fixes: 81dee67e215b ("staging: sm750fb: add sm750 to staging")
Signed-off-by: Matej Dujava <mdujava@kocurkovo.cz>
Link: https://lore.kernel.org/r/1588277366-19354-2-git-send-email-mdujava@kocurkovo.cz
